<p><a name="Awards" id="Awards"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Henri_Cartier-Bresson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: Awards">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Awards</span></h2>
<p>Cartier-Bresson is the recipient of many of prizes, awards and honorary doctorates. A partial listing of his awards:</p>
<ul>
<li>1948: Overseas Press Club of America Award</li>
<li>1953: The A.S.M.P. Award</li>
<li>1954: Overseas Press Club of America Award</li>
<li>1959: The Prix de la Société Française de Photographie</li>
<li>1960: Overseas Press Club of America Award</li>
<li>1964: Overseas Press Club of America Award</li>
<li>1974: The Culture Prize, Deutsche Gesellschaft für Photographie</li>
<li>1981: Grand Prix National de la Photographie</li>
<li>1982: <a href="/wiki/Hasselblad_Award" title="Hasselblad Award">Hasselblad Award</a></li>
<li>2006: <a href="/wiki/Prix_Nadar" title="Prix Nadar">Prix Nadar</a> for the photobook <i>Henri Cartier-Bresson: Scrapbook</i></li>
</ul>
